high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter between the stove and fridge to your left.
Grab the tomato on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge to your right.
Place the tomato in the fridge, chill the tomato and remove it.
Turn right and walk to the counter between the stove and fridge to your left.
Place the cool tomato next to the knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool tomato next to the knife on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk ahead, veering left to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Take a couple steps left to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge to the right of the potato. Close the door, wait a moment, then take it out again.
Place the tomato back on the counter, to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the middle, turn left, go to the counter with the tomato on it, left of the stove.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn left, bring the tomato to the fridge, turn right to face the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge.
Take the chilled tomato from the fridge, bring it to the counter right of the fridge.
Put the chilled tomato on the counter, left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato on the counter, left of the knife.
